# docs/Examples.pdf build scaffolding. Tracked: gen.sh (the generator) + its
# 4 static input assets (*.desc / *-spec.json) + the helper scripts that
# produced them, AND Examples.md -- the CI golden. Everything else here is a
# build artifact or scratch, regenerated by `bash gen.sh > Examples.md` then the
# pandoc command in gen.sh's header. Run with mnemonic 0.75.0 (Appendix B's
# depth-2 reconstruction is a frozen static capture -- no mnemonic-depth2 needed
# to regenerate); the committed deliverable is ../docs/Examples.pdf. Examples.md
# is git-tracked as the golden the .github/workflows/examples.yml gate diffs a
# fresh regen against (do NOT re-add it below).

# Build outputs (regenerated)
Examples.pdf
preamble.tex
*.err
work/

# Unused scratch (NOT read by gen.sh — it derives keys live + emits sections
# inline; these are earlier drafts / intermediate captures)
keys.env
*.out
H.txt
Hp.txt
knew.txt
section5.md
section6.md
section6_5.md
degrade.desc
degrade-spec.json
ex3.json
t_nums.desc
t_real.desc
tr2-bundle.json
